US_06581.longDescription:

An integral power bank means that wireless charging is also possible outside the car. The charger with integral power bank can simply be taken out of the socket for use as a mobb power bank and inductive charging point. The correct coil position for the mobb poh can be set on the side to ensure an efficient charging process. All BMW Original Accessories are tested for safety, quality and in the most demanding conditions.
